      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This car is being sold in poor overall condition and should be viewed as a fixer-upper or possible parts/project vehicle. It shows significant wear from age and use, and buyers should expect cosmetic flaws, mechanical needs, and general deferred maintenance. It is not a well-kept example, so I would recommend coming prepared to inspect it thoroughly or tow it depending on your plans. If you are looking for a low-priced project and understand it will need work, this could be worth a look.",
