      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for buyers seeking dependable transportation at an accessible price. It shows its age cosmetically, but it offers real value for someone who wants an inexpensive daily driver, starter car, or project opportunity. A straightforward, no-nonsense option priced to sell.",
