    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable transportation without spending a fortune. It\u2019s got the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect from a well-used vehicle, but it still has a lot to offer for the right buyer. A solid choice for a first car, a backup runabout, or a handy project to tidy up over time. Priced to sell and ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough old driver with plenty of life left in the platform. Shows cosmetic wear and age as expected, but the powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels planted, and it has the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes it a great budget commuter, shop truck, or weekend project. Not a showpiece, but a usable vehicle with good bones for someone who values function over perfection. Priced to move for the next owner who wants affordable transportation with real potential.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
