      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a machine with stories in its bones and plenty of opportunity for the right buyer. Whether you\u2019re after an affordable runabout, a hands-on project, or a practical set of wheels with personality, this one offers a great starting point. It has a rugged presence and the sort of lived-in charm that makes it feel like it\u2019s ready for its next chapter. If you appreciate value, potential, and a car with a little grit, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
